snippet.title: Let's Cook Together 2 – Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Let's Cook Together 2 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1637400/Lets_Cook_Together_2/

Visit https://www.letscooktogether2.com to sign up for the Closed Beta.

Embark on a gripping cooperative journey to save the planet and its food from the regime of Nutri Inc. – a powerful group of zero waste maniacs seeking to turn life on Earth into a tasteless dystopia.
